data.description: Improved price and Improvement BONU$!    Entertainers waterfront dream estate on spectacular Lake Keowee! Potential compound with full second waterfront lot included in parcel. Expansive wide-open lake and mountain views from most rooms, full-size pool with diving board, covered boat dock, jet-ski port, second dock (pier) for kayaks and paddle boards, fire pit seating area.  Lake side lawn and beaches with almost 200 feet of shoreline. Vaulted ceilings in large living room with fireplace and huge deck with outdoor living space. Second living room downstairs with fireplace and mini-kitchen/wet bar. Large master on main level with his & hers walk-in closets and jetted tub. Second bedroom on main level plus 3 beds downstairs. Bonus rooms: sun room, laundry, gym, refrigerated wine room, game room/bar/man-cave, office, storage, shed. Large garage. Finish the room above the garage into a fitness area, studio, office, etc.  Options galore!   Turn-key optional. Assumable 2.99% VA loan for qualified buyers is possible. This home is a MUST see! Note: Property CAN be short-term rented with a 90 day lease term. ***AS AN ADDED BONUS, SELLER IS OFFERING $50,000 IN A HOME IMPROVEMENT BONUS TO PAY FOR NEW KITCHEN CABINETS, COUNTERTOPS AND POOL LINER! SEE ASSOCIATED DOCUMENTS FOR KITCHEN DESIGN/QUOTE
